Upload PCAP file for analysis  /api/pcap/v1/upload/{filename}     Method:  PUT    Parameter  Data Type  Required  Description    filename  String  Yes  File name    Testing with CURL  curl 'http://www.threatlab.io/api/pcap/v1/upload/' --upload-file ~/Downloads/sample.pcap  Sample response body  {
     id :  f7c14dc9-100d-4a01-8c9e-fe7e40b7c548 
}

PCAP analysis status  /api/pcap/v1/{id}/status/       Method:  GET    Parameter  Data Type  Required  Description    id  String  Yes  Upload ID    Sample response body  {
     status :  READY 
}

Errors logged during analysis.  /api/pcap/v1/{id}/errors/       Method:  GET    Parameter  Data Type  Required  Description    id  String  Yes  Upload ID    Sample response body  {
     count : 2,
     next : null,
     previous : null,
     results : [
        {
             error :  Invalid file format ,
             tool :  SNORT ,
             pcap :  http://www.threatlab.io/api/pcap/v1/3dbcaa40-cd9b-4fdf-87ec-8cf226e582ff 
        },
        ...
    ]
}
